                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17761204-19-victim233 t17761204-19-viclabel96"></join>: the prisoner came to my shop and looked at several gowns; there was none to suit her; soon after she was gone I missed one of the gowns, and sent a person after her, but could not find her; the next day I met her in the street with the gown on; I secured her.</p>
